original_title: The Storm Chronicles: Episode 4 — Feeding Frenzy
overview: Sean Storm returns with the fourth installment of his riveting sextravaganza The Storm Chronicles: Episode 4 — Feeding Frenzy. The frenzy in this story is fired up by the pending arrival in Fort Lauderdale of Tropical Storm Oliver. Sean and his buddies are frantically getting ready for the storm and, while doing it, squeezing in just about every sex act they can think of.
tagline: Watch 8 horny guys go deep in 7 wild bareback scenes!
